precis:
Regulations Amending the MANITOBA FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1987 by expanding on
the kind of methods that may be used to give notice of a variation in close
times, in fishing quotas or in size or weight limits, to include posting
the notice on the Internet or publishing it in the Manitoba Anglers Guide
or in the Commercial Harvest Schedule.
